query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-volley',
'bluetooth-lowenergy',
'bootstrap-modal',
'bots',
'combinations',
'jax-rs',
'less',
'lstm',
'mocha',
'overflow',
'timezone',
'uiimage');
